#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about taking care of yourself.\n"
"\n"
"We often don’t look after ourselves enough. But this is so important, especially as a parent!\n"
"\n"
"Reducing our stress and treating ourselves well helps us AND our teenagers."
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje simalunga nokhathalela isiqu sakho.\n"
"\n"
"Asisoloko sizijonga ngokwaneleyo iziqu zethu. Kodwa oku kubaluleke kakhulu, ingakumbi xa ungumzali! \n"
"\n"
"Ukunciphisa uxinzelelo lwethu nokuzikhathalela kungasinceda thina KUNYE nabantwana bethu abafikisayo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_14.name’s should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Self care works! Hear @data.characters.media_female_14.name’s story"
msgstr "Ukuzikhathalela kuyasebenza! Yiva ibali lika @data.characters.media_female_14.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"For me as a parent, it was almost impossible to find time for myself. I was always busy taking care of everyone else. Through @global.app_name, I realised how important it is to take care of myself. It helps me AND my family!\n"
"\n"
"Having a moment for myself helps me to breathe and notice how I feel. Even 5 minutes to have a cup of tea makes a big difference. Now I can deal with my stress better."
msgstr ""
"Kum njengomzali, kwakunzima ukufumana ixesha lam. Ndandisoloko ndixakekekile ndikhathalela wonke umntu. Nge@global.app_name, ndiye ndabona ukuba kubaluleke kangakanani ukuzikhathalela. Iyandinceda mna KUNYE nosapho lwam! \n"
"\n"
"Ukuba nomzumzu wam kuyandinceda ndiphefumle kwaye ndiqaphele indlela endiziva ngayo. Nokuba yimizuzu emi-5 yokufumana ikomityi yeti kwenza umahluko omkhulu. Ngoku ndiyakwazi ukumelana noxinzelelo ngcono."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Taking a small break can help you feel calm and strong. But finding time is hard when you have many responsibilities.\n"
"\n"
"Support from other adults can make it easier."
msgstr ""
"Ukuthatha ikhefu elincinci kunganceda uzive uzolile kwaye unamandla. Kodwa ukufumana ixesha kunzima xana unoxanduva oluninzi.\n"
"\n"
"Inkxaso kubanye abantu abadala kungenza kubelula."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Who can you ask to help you get a short break when you need it?"
msgstr "Ngubani ongacela kuye uncedo lokufumana ikhefu elifutshane xana ulidinga?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Family member"
msgstr "Ilungu losapho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great!"
msgstr "Kulunge kakhulu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Another caregiver"
msgstr "Omnye umnakekeli"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fantastic!"
msgstr "Kwakuhle kakhulu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Friend"
msgstr "Umhlobo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Wonderful!"
msgstr "Kuhle oko!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Someone else"
msgstr "Omnye umntu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Excellent!"
msgstr "Ugqwesile!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How can caregivers at home support each other to take a break?"
msgstr "Ingaba abanakekeli emakhaya bangaxhasana njani ekuthatheni ikhefu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remind them of easy ways to take care of themselves"
msgstr "Bakhumbuze ngendlela ezilula zokuzikhathalela"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Help them find time to relax by offering to assist with chores or childcare"
msgstr "Bancede bafumane ixesha lokuphumla ngobanika uncedo ngemisebenzi yasekhaya okanye ukhathalela umntwana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Find moments of play and laughter together"
msgstr "Fumana amathuba okudlala nokuhleka kunye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly! When caregivers help each other take small breaks, everyone in the family benefits. Teens also learn that self-care is important."
msgstr "Kanye-kanye! Xana abanakekeli bencedana ukuthatha ikhefu elincinci, wonke umntu wosapho uyaxhamla. Abantwana abafikisayo nabo bayafunda ukuba ukuzinakekela kubalulekile."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Appreciating ourselves is one way to care for ourselves. \n"
"\n"
"Let’s give it a try."
msgstr ""
"Ukuzincoma kwethu yindlela enye yokukhathela iziqu zethu. \n"
"\n"
"Makhe siyizameni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Think of one thing YOU have done well recently.\n"
"\n"
"\"Well done to me for...\""
msgstr ""
"Cinga ngento ibenye WENA ubukhe wayenza kakuhle kutshanje.\n"
"\n"
"\"Ndiqhube kakuhle ngokwenza...\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Showing love to my children"
msgstr "Bonisa uthando ebantwaneni bam"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Getting up even though I felt tired"
msgstr "Ukuvuka nangona ndiziva ndidiniwe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Smiling at someone"
msgstr "Ukuncumela umntu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Making food to stay strong"
msgstr "Ukwenza ukutya ukuze uhlale womelele"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Spending time with my children"
msgstr "Ukuchitha ixesha nabantwana bam"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Helping my children with schoolwork"
msgstr "Ukuncedisa abantwana bam kumsebenzi wesikolo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say it aloud if you can.\n"
"\n"
"Here is one thing you deserve praise for: Well done for using @global.app_name!"
msgstr ""
"Yitsho ngokuvakalayo ukuba unako.\n"
"\n"
"Nantsi into enye ofanelwe kukunconywa ngayo: Uqhube kakuhle ngokusebenzisa i-@global.app_name!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some tips to help you take care of yourself."
msgstr "Nazi ezinye ingcebiso ezinokunceda wena ukhathalele isiqu sakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "RELAX"
msgstr "PHOLA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do a 30 second quick relaxation activity."
msgstr "Yenza umsebenzi oza kukupholisa okhawulezileyo wemizuzu engama-30."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Take a moment now to relax. Breathe in slowly as you count to three... and breathe out as you count to three. Feel your body relax with each breath. \n"
"\n"
"Try this whenever you are feeling stressed and need a break. A few calm breaths can make a big difference."
msgstr ""
"Thatha imizuzwana ngoku uphole. Bizela umphefumlo ngokucotha ube ubala uyokutsho kwisithathu... phinda uphefumlele ngaphandle ube ubala uyokutsho kwisithathu. Yiva umzimba wakho upholile ngomphemfulo ngamnye.\n"
"\n"
"Zama lento nanina uziva unoxinzelelo ube ufuna ukuphumla. Ukuphefumla ngokuzola kambalwa kungenza umehluko omkhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "RECOGNISE"
msgstr "QAPHELA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Think of one thing YOU have done well recently.\n"
"\n"
"_\"Well done to me for...\"_"
msgstr ""
"Cinga ngento ibenye WENA ubukhe wayenza kakuhle kutshanje.\n"
"\n"
"_\"Kum ndiqhube kakuhle ngokwenza...\"_"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It could be showing love to your children, helping them with schoolwork, or preparing a meal even when you felt tired. \n"
"\n"
"Every small effort you make matters, and you get to celebrate yourself."
msgstr ""
"Ingakubonisa uthando kubantwana bakho, ukubancedisa ngemisebenzi yesikolo, okanye ubalungiselele ukutya naxa uziva udiniwe.\n"
"\n"
"Yonke imzamo emincinci oyenzayo, kwaye ufumane ukuzibhoyozela."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REWARD"
msgstr "UMVUZO"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, you deserve your “me time” too! What makes you happy?"
msgstr "Khumbula, ufanelwe \"lixesha lakho\" nawe! Yintoni ekwenza wonwabe?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It could be something small, like enjoying a cup of tea, taking a short nap, chatting with a friend, or listening to your favourite music.\n"
"\n"
"Spending time with your teen can be fun for you too! It might even make you feel less stressed."
msgstr ""
"Ingayinto encinci, njengo konwabela ikomityi ye-ti, ukungqengqa kancinci, uncokole nomhlobo, okanye umamele umculo owuthandayo.\n"
"\n"
"Ukuchitha ixesha kunye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kungakonwabisa nawe! Ingakwenza uzive unoxinzelelo oluphantsi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SUPPORT"
msgstr "INKXASO"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Help other caregivers, including your partner, to take care of themselves, and ask them to do the same for you."
msgstr "Nceda abanye abanakekeli, ukuquka nomlingane wakho, ukuba bazikhathalele, kwaye ubacele benze okufanayo kuwe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye iingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Share chores, give each other time to rest, or remind each other to take breaks. When caregivers support each other, the whole community benefits — and teens learn self-care matters, too."
msgstr "Yabelanani ngomsebenzi, ninikane ixesha lokuphumla, okanye nikhumbuzane ukuba nithathe ikhefu. Xa abanakekeli bexhasana, bonke abahlali bayazuza - kwaye abantwana abafikisayo bafunda ukuzikhathalela nabo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Treating ourselves well is another way of looking after ourselves.\n"
"\n"
"You can give yourself a small reward every day, and it does not have to cost a thing!"
msgstr ""
"Ukuziphatha kakuhle iziqu zethu yenye yendlela yokujongana neziqu zethu.\n"
"\n"
"Ungasinika isiqu sakho umvuzo omncinci mihla yonke, kwaye akunyanzelekanga ibe lixabiso lanto!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What small thing makes you happy?"
msgstr "Yintoni encinci ekwenza wonwabe?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sleeping"
msgstr "Ukulala"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talking with a friend"
msgstr "Ukuthetha nomhlobo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Reading something I enjoy"
msgstr "Ukufunda into endiyonwabelayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Going for a walk"
msgstr "Ukuthatha uhambo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Having a nice cup of coffee, tea or hot chocolate"
msgstr "Ufumane ikomityi ye kofu, iti okanye itshokolethi eshushu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Something else"
msgstr "Enye into"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nice! Taking care of yourself is an important parenting skill!"
msgstr "Kuhle! Ukuzikhathalela sisakhono esibalulekileyo sobuzali!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Remember: Small moments of self-care matter. This week, find time to relax, recognize your efforts, and reward yourself whenever you can.\n"
" \n"
"Care for yourself every day. You deserve it!"
msgstr ""
"Khumbula: Imizuzwana emincinci yokuzi khathalela kubalulekile. Kule veki, fumana ithuba lokuphola, qaphela imizamo yakho kwaye uzivuze kangangoko unako.\n"
" \n"
"Zikhathalele yonke imihla. Ukufanele oko!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you find moments this week to relax, recognise your efforts, and reward yourself?"
msgstr "Ungafumana imizuzwana kule veki uphole, qaphela imizamo yakho, kwaye uzinike imvuzo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Every small step you take to care for yourself makes a big difference for your family."
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu! Qho usenza inyathelo elincinci ngokukhathalela isiqu sakho wenza umehluko omkhulu kusapho lwakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s a good start! Look for small ways to relax, recognise your efforts, and reward yourself - even little moments of self-care can make a big difference."
msgstr "Sisiqalo esilungileyo! Khangela indlela ezincinci zokuphola, qaphela imizamo yakho, kwaye uzivuze- nemizuzwana nje embalwa yokuzikhathalela ingenza umehluko omkhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Try choosing one small, simple action like taking a deep breath or sitting quietly for a moment. Every little bit counts!"
msgstr "Kulungile, Zama ukukhetha ibenye encinci, ukwenza nje into elula uphefumle nzulu okanye uhlale ngokuzola umzuzwana. Yonke into encinci iyabala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Remember, taking small moments for self-care helps us stay calm, strong, and connected to our families. \n"
"\n"
"When we look after ourselves, we are better able to support our teens!"
msgstr ""
"Khumbula, ukuthatha imizuzwana emincinci ngesiqu sakho kuyasinceda sihlale sizolile, somelele kwaye siqhagamshelene nentsapho zethu.\n"
"\n"
"Xa sizijonga iziqu zethu, singakwazi ngcono ukuxhasa abantwana bethu abafikisayo!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_son_5.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Listen to what @data.characters.media_son_5.name says about his father practising self care"
msgstr "Mamela into etshiwo ngu @data.characters.media_son_5.name malunga no tata wakhe ezama ukuzikhathalela"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @global.app_name
#.      @global.app_name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"My dad was always busy. He would come home from work and snap at us when we started asking him questions.\n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name helped us a lot. We no longer fight. Now, when my dad comes home, he first sits down by himself for 5 minutes and then we do a relaxing activity from @global.app_name together, so we can all take a deep breath and relax. Then we can chat about our day, about anything good or bad that happened. Everyone is so much happier now."
msgstr ""
"Utata wam wayehlala exakekile. Wayebuya emsebenzini asiphoxe xa siqala ukumbuza imibuzo.\n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name yasinceda kakhulu. Asisalwi. Ngoku, utata xa efika endlini, uqala azihlalelele imizuzu eyi-5 emva koko senze umsebenzi wokuphumla kwi@global.app_name sisonke,siye siphefumle nzulu kwaye siphole. Emva koko sincokole ngosuku lwethu,malunga nezinto ezintle okanye ezimbi ezithe zenzeka. Wonke umntu wonwabile kakhulu ngoku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You’re almost done! Let’s check in."
msgstr "Sele uzokugqiba! Masingene."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you feel now?"
msgstr "Uziva njani ngoku?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Happy"
msgstr "Bayavuya"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s great to hear! Keep doing what helps you feel strong. Even small moments for yourself make a big difference."
msgstr "Kulungile ukuva oko! Qhubekeka usenza into ezakunceda uzive womelele. Nokuba ngamathuba amancinci wesiqu sakho enza umahluko omkhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay"
msgstr "Kulungile"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thanks for checking in. “Okay” is a good start. Maybe try one small thing today just for you, like a short break or deep breath."
msgstr "Enkosi ngokungena. \"Kulungile\" sisiqalo esilungileyo. Mhlawumbi zama ukuzenzela into encinci namhlanje, njengekhefu elifitshane okanye uphefumlele ezantsi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr "Ulusizi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I’m glad you shared that. Remember, self-care keeps you strong for yourself and your family. Try one calming thing from this module or talk to someone you trust."
msgstr "Ndiyavuya wabelane ngalonto. Khumbula, ukunakekela isiqu sakho kugcina wena uqinile kunye nosapho lwakho. Zama enye into ezolileyo esuka kule modyuli okanye uthethe nomntu omthembayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle ngokuthatha ixesha lesiqu sakho namhlanje. 🎉"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr "Nali ushicilelo olufutshane elizokunceda wehlise ngaphambi kokuba uhambe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
"Xa yonke into ivakala ingathi iyamoshakala Kwaye awukwazi ukuzinceda uvele unyuse ilizwi Xa zonke iinzingo ziqala Khumbula ukuba ungenza ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sehlise kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba andinakuthanda ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Yima, ungabala uyokutsho ku 10 Dlala umdlalo okanye wenze into emnandi Ungafowunela umhlobo, umntu onokumchazela ingxaki Khumbula ayinguwe wedwa\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi \n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsalaa umoya Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsalaa umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi"

